channel.title: My own RsPs Giveaway!
channel.description:
Alright guyis so im giving out my server for someone to be hosted because i cannot host it myself due to the fact i have bad internet connection :P
The server has Dungeoneering, Full summoning (creating pouches etc....), We also have different auras,pets,titles,Torva,Virtus,Pernix (with hp effect ;)), all Chaotics,SoF (squel of fortune), Awesome donator only options including Donator Chest and Donator Island :). Only thing you need to do when i give it to you is to make me a CO-owner and change the name and ip of the server and put it online ofc :P PS: We also have making overloads and spec restores :D
